<bibRefCitation author="ASSING V" box="[577,725,368,390]" pageId="5" pageNumber="28" pagination="33 - 82" refId="ref6826" refString="ASSING V. (2004 a): A revision of the Medon species of the Eastern Mediterranean and adjacent regions (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Bonner zoologische Beitrage 52: 33 - 82." type="journal article" year="2004">ASSING 2004a</bibRefCitation>
