<bibRefCitation author="ASSING V" box="[736,804,368,390]" pageId="5" pageNumber="28" pagination="655 - 662" refId="ref6867" refString="ASSING V. (2004 b): A revision of Western Palaearctic Medon STEPHENS (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae, Paederinae). Supplement I. - Linzer biologische Beitrage 36 (2): 655 - 662." type="journal article" year="2004">2004b</bibRefCitation>
); it is here reported from western 
<collectingCountry box="[236,323,398,420]" name="Turkey" pageId="5" pageNumber="28">Anatolia</collectingCountry>
for the first time.
